700
01:05:36,900 --> 01:05:39,100
Jake has this ugly
old dog and he...

701
01:05:41,300 --> 01:05:43,200
What am I doing?

702
01:05:43,200 --> 01:05:45,100
You don't understand
a word I say.

703
01:05:47,500 --> 01:05:48,400
Yagaichi.

704
01:05:57,100 --> 01:05:59,400
Washakie: When the summer
moved into fall,

705
01:05:59,400 --> 01:06:02,800
