to escape the heavy snows.

706
01:06:05,400 --> 01:06:08,600
Yagaichi traveled with us
at a difficult time.

707
01:06:09,600 --> 01:06:11,800
As the snow
came early that y ear,

708
01:06:11,800 --> 01:06:14,500
the hunting grounds
were scarce.

709
01:06:15,400 --> 01:06:17,600
