Is what the sky
has told me.

713
01:06:41,100 --> 01:06:42,600
(signaling)

714
01:07:11,500 --> 01:07:12,900
So?

715
01:07:12,900 --> 01:07:15,100
Crows come.
Fight.

716
01:07:15,100 --> 01:07:16,500
Isn't that good?

717
01:07:16,600 --> 01:07:19,500
I do not like fight.

718
01:07:19,500 --> 01:07:22,200
No good comes.
But Crows

719
01:07:22,100 --> 01:07:24,200
will take our horses,

720
