779
01:17:08,100 --> 01:17:12,400
He'd be about 15 now.

780
01:17:12,300 --> 01:17:14,200
Maybe near my height,

781
01:17:14,200 --> 01:17:16,100
light colored hair,
blue eyes.

782
01:17:16,100 --> 01:17:18,600
